title: [Graveyard Temporalis, Outer Rim]
description: While the red-veined vines tangle and twist around the iron fence topping the stone wall, small clusters of greenery with multi-blossomed sprigs of skeleton flowers peek from the low-lying ground fog.  Tendrils of mist meander along the wall, with the occasional thin finger reaching to trail along the mortar between the stones in the wall.  A wan, frail flicker of light burns to the east.
